&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tips&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you met a bug while using, you can open an issue &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/vuepress-theme-hope/vuepress-theme-hope/issues&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
